  92,1,"aqsm allah subhanah biallayl eindama yughatiy bzlamh al'ard wama elyha, wbalnhar 'iidha ainkashaf ean zlam allayl bdyayh, wbkhlq alzwjyn: aldhikr walantha. 'iina eamalukum limukhtalif bayn eamil lldnya weaml llakhrt"
  92,2,"aqsm allah subhanah biallayl eindama yughatiy bzlamh al'ard wama elyha, wbalnhar 'iidha ainkashaf ean zlam allayl bdyayh, wbkhlq alzwjyn: aldhikr walantha. 'iina eamalukum limukhtalif bayn eamil lldnya weaml llakhrt"
  92,3,"aqsm allah subhanah biallayl eindama yughatiy bzlamh al'ard wama elyha, wbalnhar 'iidha ainkashaf ean zlam allayl bdyayh, wbkhlq alzwjyn: aldhikr walantha. 'iina eamalukum limukhtalif bayn eamil lldnya weaml llakhrt"
